snippet.title: ANIMALS GO TO THE VET: Funniest REACTIONS - You'll LAUGH ALL DAY LONG
snippet.description:
Sometimes animals need to visit animal doctor, so called the vet. And just like humans, animals don't like doctors. Just look how all these cats and dogs react to vet visits. They make funny sounds, they hide, get angry and so on. Quite funny isn't it? What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
